      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Vanessa joined the MHRA as Director of Human Resources in January 2015.</p>

<p>Immediately prior to her appointment she was the Strategic Head of Human Resources for Virgin Care; a private provider of NHS community services across England. Vanessa joined Virgin Care three years previously, following several years in Human Resources Director roles in a variety of NHS organisations and a career in Human Resources within the NHS which spans a total of over 20 years. Her Director portfolios included a range of other corporate responsibilities, such as communications, health & safety and business planning.</p>

<p>Vanessa is a Fellow of the Chartered Institute of Personnel and has a Masters Degree in Human Resources Management.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_2482">
            <h1 id="director-of-human-resources">Director of Human Resources</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Our HR division works with <abbr title="Medicines and Healthcare Products Regulatory Agency">MHRA</abbr> managers and staff to provide professional and efficient HR services including continuous learning and development. This is achieved by:</p>

<ul>
  <li>ensuring that all <abbr title="Medicines and Healthcare Products Regulatory Agency">MHRA</abbr> staff are provided with an HR policy framework that is clear, up to date and accessible</li>
  <li>providing accurate, consistent advice and support on HR policies and procedures within reasonable time</li>
  <li>enabling effective leadership and improving the overall performance of the organisation</li>
  <li>developing people to be committed and skilled to achieve the agencyâ€™s objectives and enjoy shared success</li>
</ul>

